    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4a.26a.45"/>
                
                <fw type="curatorial">45</fw>
                
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        Columbia, Missouri
                        April 22, I958<sic>1958</sic>
                    </dateline>
                    
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>Dr. John <hi rend="caps">G.</hi> Neihardt &amp; Family</addrLine>
                            <addrLine>Columbia, <hi rend="caps">R.</hi> #7</addrLine>
                    </address>
                    
                    <salute>Dear friends:-</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>Mrs. Ferguson joins me in expressing our deepest sympathy in the passing of Mrs Neihardt, who will be greatly missed by all who knew her,- a personality admired and worthy of inculcating into the lives of others.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute><hi rend="caps">VERY</hi> respt'y<sic>respectfully</sic> yours</salute>
                    
                    <signed>Leon Ferguson</signed>
                </closer>
                
            </div1>
        </body>
        
